<!DOCTYPE html>
<html ng-app="sharikiApp">
	<head>
		<title><%= title %></title>
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<link href="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen">
		<link href="//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Molle:400italic" rel="stylesheet">
		<link href="/stylesheets/flat-ui.css" rel="stylesheet">
		<link rel='shortcut icon' href="/images/landing/logo_v3.png" type='image/x-icon'>
		<link rel='icon' href="/images/landing/logo_v3.png" type='image/x-icon'>
		<link href="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.0.3/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
		<link href="/stylesheets/custom.css" rel="stylesheet">
		<link href="/stylesheets/about.css" rel="stylesheet">
	</head>
	<body ng-controller="RoomListCtrl">
		<!-- Navigation -->
		<nav class="navbar navbar-default" role="navigation">
			<div class="navbar-header">
				<button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbar-collapse-01">
				<span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
				</button>
				<a class="navbar-brand welcome" href="/">hulabuk</a>
			</div>
			<div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbar-collapse-01">
				<ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
					<li class="active"><a href="/about">about</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</nav>

		<!-- Content -->
		<div class="container">
		  <div class="row">
		        <div class="col-md-5">
		          <h3>Contact us</h3>
		          <p>Have any questions or interested in partnership with us? Drop us an email at <strong>team@hulabuk.com</strong> and our dedicated team will get back to you.</p>

		          <h3>About us</h3>
		          <h5 class="green-text">Outsmart hotels in their own game</h5>
		          <p>Hotels have been playing their pricing game for too long and it's just about time for travelers to get the control. <strong>hulabuk</strong> is all about smart hotel search - we bring transparency on hotel prices and educate travelers on finding truly <strong>best deals</strong>. Our powerful <strong>Dealchart</strong> lets you compare prices on any room for any dates in the most efficient way. hulabuk makes you smart - and smart traveler is a happy traveler.</p>

		          <h5 class="green-text">No crossed out prices</h5>
		          <p>Hotels love showing those. How do you know this "deal" you are shown is the real deal? hulabuk doesn't give you crossed out prices. It just gives you the <strong>lowest prices you can find anywhere</strong>. That comes with the Best Price Guarantee.</p>
		      </div>
		      <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-6">
		        <h3>Your opinion</h3>
		        <p class="green-text"><strong>We are young and growing and we love to hear feedback. Tell us what you think.</strong></p>
		        
		        <form novalidate name="feedbackForm" role="form">
		          <div class="form-group" ng-class="{'has-error': feedbackForm.email.$invalid && (feedbackForm.email.$dirty || submitAttempted)}">
		            <input required name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Type in your e-mail here" type="email" ng-model="fromEmail"></input>
		          </div>
		          <p>How useful is hulabuk to you?</p>
		          
		          <div class="form-group">
		          <h4>
		            <span class="glyphicon glyph-rating" ng-click="updateStars($index)" ng-repeat="star in stars track by $index" ng-class="star ? 'glyphicon-star' : 'glyphicon-star-empty'"></span>
		          </h4>
		          </div>

		          <div class="form-group">
		            <textarea ng-model="features" class="form-control" rows="4" placeholder="Which cities do you want to see on hulabuk next?"></textarea>
		          </div>

		          <div class="form-group">
		            <textarea ng-model="good" class="form-control" rows="4" placeholder="What is good about hulabuk?"></textarea>
		          </div>

		          <div class="form-group">
		            <textarea ng-model="better" class="form-control" rows="4" placeholder="What can we do better?"></textarea>
		          </div>

		          <div class="form-group">
		            <button type="button" ng-click="submitFeedback()" class="btn btn-wide btn-primary btn-block">Send your feedback</button>
		          </div>

		          <div class="form-group">
		            <div ng-show="feedbackSuccess && feedbackMessage" class="ng-cloak alert alert-success">{{ feedbackMessage }}</div>
		          </div>

		          <div class="form-group">
		            <div ng-show="!feedbackSuccess && feedbackMessage" class="ng-cloak alert alert-danger">{{ feedbackMessage }}</div>
		          </div>

		        </form> 
		      </div>
		  </div>
		</div>

		<!-- Scripts -->
		<script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
		<script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jqueryui/1.10.4/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
		<script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.2.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
		<script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery-placeholder/2.0.7/jquery.placeholder.js"></script>
		<script src="/javascripts/bootstrap-select.js"></script>
		<script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/angular.js/1.2.12/angular.min.js"></script>
		<script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/angular-ui-bootstrap/0.11.0/ui-bootstrap-tpls.min.js"></script>	
		<script src="/javascripts/application.js"></script>
		<script>
		  (function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){
		  (i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o),
		  m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m)
		  })(window,document,'script','//www.google-analytics.com/analytics.js','ga');

		  ga('create', 'UA-50435179-2', 'hulabuk.com');
		  ga('send', 'pageview');

		</script>
		<script src="/javascripts/controllers.js"></script>
	</body>
</html>